author: dims
msg: Fix problem with wrong usage of WeakHashMap's. Entries get kicked out when the Keys are GC'ed. Now using WeakReference to make sure EndpointDescriptionImpl's stored in AxisConfiguration are still GC'able.
Many Thanks to Chris Whyley for finding this issue!

author: clement
msg: Create an empty Hashtable when parsing an empty aggregate property element. This allows specifying empty dictionaries inside instance configurations. The instance configuration, then, receives an empty dictionary for this property.
